Invocation Name: craft life
des:
Craft Life Brewing started as a way to share Tim's awesome beer with the world, starting in Land O' Lakes. We have been embraced by the community and have grown to be a local live music venue as well as a place to hang and enjoy delicious craft beer. Our focus is local and our offerings cater to that concept featuring local music talent and Florida craft breweries. We cannot know the future but look forward to enjoying it with you all.

You can ask Alexa for our hours, location, about us, founding membership, contact us, food, music, whats on tap
